data.description: WELCOME HOME! Stunning, well maintained 3 bedroom/2.5 bath townhouse in sought after Amberly Mill is a MUST SEE with NO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS! This spacious corner unit features a large kitchen complete with granite countertops, abundant cabinet space, a pantry, a huge kitchen island and stainless steel appliances (all included), hardwood floors throughout the main level, large family room with gas fireplace and lots of natural light, and an open concept dining area! Upstairs there is an oversized master suite featuring a tray ceiling and a spa-like master bathroom with double vanity, soaking tub, separate shower and a sizable master closet. Convenient upstairs laundry room and two additional bedrooms, each with ample closet space, complete the upstairs. The backyard patio faces the woods creating an ideal space for relaxing. Two car attached garage, along with a large driveway, allow for plenty of parking possibilities. You will love all this home has to offer. It's simply beautiful! Convenient access to I-85, 285 & 316. Within minutes of Northside Gwinnett Hospital, Shopping & Dining.
